# PCA   : () . 
pca = PCA(n_components = 500 # 100  .
          , whiten = True
          , random_state = 0).fit(X_train)
                             # fit(X_train)
                             #   (y_train) .
X_train_pca = pca.transform(X_train)
X_test_pca = pca.transform(X_test)

print("X_train_pca.shape : {}".format(X_train_pca.shape)) # 100 


##     (knn)
knn = KNeighborsClassifier(n_neighbors = 1)
knn.fit(X_train_pca, y_train)
print("   : {:.2}".format(knn.score(X_test_pca, y_test)))
